<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="21" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="21">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="21">
This species is named in honour of retired Prof. Dr. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Şinasi">Sinasi</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Yıldırımlı">Yildirimli</normalizedToken>
(Biology Dep. Hacettepe University, Turkey), who is an expert in Plant systematics and taxonomy. He described more than 100 new plant species for science in Turkey. The Turkish name of this species is given as &quot;Levent 
<normalizedToken originalValue="İplikçiği”">Iplikcigi&quot;</normalizedToken>
, according to the guidelines of 
